10 An act relating to the local media advertising tax credit
11 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
12 Sec. 1. 32 V.S.A. § 5813 is amended to read:
13 § 5813. STATUTORY PURPOSES
14 * * *
15 (aa) The statutory purpose of the local media advertising tax credit in
16 section 5830g of this title is to provide an incentive to small businesses to
17 advertise with local media outlets.
18 Sec. 2. 32 V.S.A. § 5830g is added to read:
19 § 5830g. LOCAL MEDIA ADVERTISING TAX CREDIT
